# Build and Lint

After every code change, run goimports on the changed files, then run build and lint:

```bash
make build
make lint
```

- `make build` compiles the binary and validates test compilation.
- `make lint` runs `golangci-lint` to check for issues.
- If lint errors are found, fix them before considering the task complete.
- Use `make lint-fix` to auto-fix lint issues when appropriate.
